[Malaria is endemic in Colon province, which is mainly low land along the coast to the Caribbean. In 2010 Honduras reported 9216 positive malaria slides, of which 1283 were _Plasmodium falciparum_ and 7834 were _P. vivax_.

The Department of Colon had 284 900 people in 2007 (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Col%C3%B3n_Department_(Honduras)). â€“ Mod.EP

